{"tid":1430820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]希望各位手足今日可以喺屋企同爸爸媽媽一齊睇民間記招","createTime":"2019-08-08T00:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:59:54.000Z","uid":176313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e83646b69a395040f2677189ad18f1bcf8c6ce4","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:03:56.000Z","msg":"由於老一輩平時一般都係睇cctvb，資訊唔對等嘅情況下，會有好多講唔清嘅爭拗。而民間記招嘅作用之一，就係釐清事實，講出道理，可以話係一個強大嘅文宣活動。所以如果各位手足屋企有藍絲父母，其實呢個係一個說服佢哋嘅好機會。<br />\n所以希望大家如果唔使翻工，就盡量主動搵父母一齊睇live，等佢哋了解真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a16c0a7143ef169201efd2ea3fa76e1c7b441e","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8521f6995b50865af3d1961ba79d81c901e15922","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3020d5e9e90baec801b383c22ad2e5dacc4541e5","tid":1430820,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:14:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"acb4f2a0562161f016ecc94b31eb642cde0480f0","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebdbae7901e5cacd4897b32435038fcdecad0728","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0334cad6b23c48af90e00f0a6f5b86962c69f0c","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bc2a76dd0cf2627137b367e428404081b595770","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76fe0d95d7112128da38f4b55a62044a106f7892","tid":1430820,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ee0f0f19965ec999d0a1a81c947